data.description: This stunning 4-bedroom, 3.5-bathroom house is a true gem, offering a spacious and comfortable living environment with numerous upgrades and special features. Enjoy the luxury of four spacious bedrooms,  3 full bathrooms and a convenient half-bath. This home boasts numerous upgrades, including new flooring and remodeled bathrooms. The open and inviting great room is perfect for gatherings and entertaining, featuring high ceilings and an abundance of space. Formal Living Room and Family Room offer a choice between two comfortable living spaces for relaxation and entertainment. The spa room with hot tub offers a place to relax and unwind after work. An office/library also provides more living space. Step outside to a massive backyard with lush landscaping. A composite deck provides the perfect spot for outdoor dining and entertaining. Additional storage space is available with a convenient shed, and your furry friends will love their own cozy doghouse.
